data.description: Amazing opportunity to own just under 6 unrestricted acres in the highly sought after Paradise ISD with a charming 3 bed 2 bath barndominium and oversized shop. As you walk in the front door of this beautiful home, enjoy the open floor plan, recently upgraded flooring, and new paint throughout. With a HUGE primary suite and split floor plan this home offers the ideal floor plan. This property boast a 30x40 shop with 27ft covered overhang, water, sewer, and direct tv available in the shop. Also included on this beautiful property is a 50 AMP RV hook up and septic system. With no deed restrictions, this is the perfect place to bring your animals and enjoy country living on this beautiful slice of Paradise!
